                <head>Nationality of Children born of Alien Parents.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Foreign Office</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-08-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">August</hi> 11 1868</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The accompanying circular was sent from the foreign office to her Majesty’s
                    representatives at European courts:</p>
                <p>“I have to instruct you to furnish me with a report for the information of the
                    Naturalization Commission on the state of the——law with regard to the
                    nationality of children born of alien parents within the——dominions.”</p>
            </div>
